[23/12/2018 02:45:54] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[23/12/2018 02:45:55] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, Marco.</font>
[23/12/2018 02:45:56] <font color="#ffffff">¿Qué tal?</font>
[23/12/2018 02:46:01] <font color="#ffff00">Alexandre Andlauer es analista</font>
